<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>Conteúdo indisponível - <%- title %></title>
		<style>
			body {
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
				font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
				background: #f8fafc;
				color: #0f172a;
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: center;
				min-height: 100vh;
			}
			main {
				max-width: 640px;
				background: #ffffff;
				padding: 24px;
				border-radius: 12px;
				border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
				box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
			}
			h1 {
				margin-top: 0;
				font-size: 22px;
			}
			p {
				line-height: 1.6;
				color: #334155;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<main>
			<h1><%- title %></h1>
			<p><%- description %></p>
			<p>O vídeo final desta aula não está disponível neste pacote SCORM.</p>
		</main>

		<script src="scorm_api_wrapper.js"></script>
		<script>
			window.onload = function () {
				scorm.init();
				scorm.setStatus('completed');
				scorm.setScore(100);
				scorm.save();
			};
		</script>
	</body>
</html>
